string_data: A Just Stop Oil environmental activist stands on an airport tarmac at Stansted Airport, posing in front of a private jet that has been covered in bright orange paint. The person is wearing a white shirt with "JUST STOP OIL" text and holding what appears to be protest materials. The aircraft, operated by Harrods Aviation according to visible signage, is completely doused in orange paint as part of the environmental protest action.
